Chocolate-Strawberry.name: Chocolate-Strawberry
Chocolate-Strawberry.description: Chocolate genoise w/ chocolate whipped cream & strawberries. Topped with chocolate ganache drip, strawberries and chocolate truffles.

Classic Strawberry Cream.name: Classic Strawberry Cream
Classic Strawberry Cream.description: Vanilla sponge w/ whipped cream & strawberries. *Strawberry Whipcream available!

Devon Cream (Victorian Sponge).name: Devon Cream (Victorian Sponge)
Devon Cream (Victorian Sponge).description: A take on british-style scones w/ devon cream + raspberry jam, mixed with a classic victorian sponge cake.

Lemon Cake.name: Lemon Cake
Lemon Cake.description: Basically a Lemon Bundt Cake, but minus the Bundt Shape! Topped w/ candied lemons and lemon icing.

Milk Tea Coffee Crunch.name: Milk Tea Coffee Crunch
Milk Tea Coffee Crunch.description: Black tea sponge cake filled with milk tea flavored whipped cream and coffee crisp chocolate for extra texture. Masked with coffee flavored whipped ganache, and finished w/ whipped cream dollops.

Mint Chocolate.name: Mint Chocolate
Mint Chocolate.description: Chocolate genoise sponge-cake, mint-flavored whipped cream (stablized w/ a little bit of white chocolate), with dark chocolate ganache filling. Garnished with chocolate covered mint leaves, gold leaves, and a chocolate ring.

Peach Oolong (*Earl Grey Alternative).name: Peach Oolong (*Earl Grey Alternative)
Peach Oolong (*Earl Grey Alternative).description: Oolong flavored genoise sponge. Cooked white peach filling and oolong insert cream. Garnished with more white peaches, rose petals and jasmine petals. FROZEN PEACHES USED on off seasons!

Strawberry-Matcha.name: Strawberry-Matcha
Strawberry-Matcha.description: Matcha genoise sponge w/ strawberry whipped cream and strawberry slices. Royce-style matcha truffle chocolates (nama-chocolate) as added decoration!

Tea-Flavored Pound Cake.name: Tea-Flavored Pound Cake
Tea-Flavored Pound Cake.description: Matcha, Double Cream Earl Grey, Black Tea (Orange Pekoe), Various other black-tea flavors that I haven't tried yet!

Very Berry Custard.name: Very Berry Custard
Very Berry Custard.description: Vanilla sponge w/ a custard cream filling & home-made berry jam (raspberries, blueberries, blackberries, strawberries).

(Orange) Chocolate Tart.name: (Orange) Chocolate Tart
(Orange) Chocolate Tart.description: Dark or milk chocolate ganache filling, flavored with rum and a bit of orange extract. Topped with a cocoa glaze and edible gold. (For future orders, maybe orange zest!) *Orange flavoring is optional, if you prefer just a plain chocolate tart

Peachy-Apple Custard.name: Peachy-Apple Custard
Peachy-Apple Custard.description: Sugar-syrup'd applie slices on top of a peach-oolong jam, and custard filling.

Red N' Berries.name: Red N' Berries
Red N' Berries.description: An all-red, berry tart (strawberries, raspberries, cherries) w/ a chocolate crust.

Sweet Potato Montblanc.name: Sweet Potato Montblanc
Sweet Potato Montblanc.description: A montblanc tart, but with japanese sweet potato puree instead of chestnut!

(Easter) Brownies.name: (Easter) Brownies
(Easter) Brownies.description: Cabury mini-egg brownies! Secret ingredient: Espresso!

Ube Leche Flan Cupcakes.name: Ube Leche Flan Cupcakes
Ube Leche Flan Cupcakes.description: Ube cupcakes topped with mini Leche Flans and whipped cream! Decorated to resemble daisies.

Valentine Gift Box (A) *Seasonal.name: Valentine Gift Box (A) *Seasonal
Valentine Gift Box (A) *Seasonal.description: Comes w/ (2pcs) of Reg. Nama-Choco, (2pcs) Matcha Nama-Choco, (1-2pc) Freeze-Dried Strawberry Truffle, (1-2pc) Pistachio Truffle, 3pc Icebox Cookies (Cranberry, Earl Grey, Matcha)

Valentine Gift Box (B) *Seasonal.name: Valentine Gift Box (B) *Seasonal
Valentine Gift Box (B) *Seasonal.description: Comes w/ Assorted Butter Cookies & (3pcs) Truffles (Regular, Orange-Marmalade, Red-Velvet)
